# Lucide React Best Practices

## Context

- Provides guidelines for consistent icon usage across the project
- Ensures proper icon implementation and accessibility
- Helps maintain visual consistency and performance

## Critical Rules

- Use Lucide icons for a consistent and modern iconography
- Import only the icons you need to reduce bundle size
- Customize icon sizes and colors using Tailwind CSS classes
- Ensure icons are accessible by providing appropriate alt text
- Keep icon usage consistent across the application for a cohesive look
- Use semantic icon names that match their purpose
- Implement proper icon sizing for different contexts
- Use consistent icon styling patterns

